text: b'RT @RainyDay: I still fall for you everyday.'
b'It hurts until it doesn\xe2\x80\x99t.'
b'RT @RainyDay: You can\xe2\x80\x99t rush something you want to last forever.'
b'RT @RainyDay: You make this life worth living.'
b'Find what you love and let it kill you.'
b'Some days you don\xe2\x80\x99t want to feel at all.'
b'Give me all of you, the same way you want all of me.'
b'I\xe2\x80\x99d rather be sad with you than happy with someone else.'
b'It\xe2\x80\x99s exhausting, always missing you.'
b'I broke my own heart trying to be enough for you.'
b'I miss the way you used to smile for me.'
b'I\xe2\x80\x99m sorry to the people I hurt while I was hurting.'
b'Maybe if my heart stops beating it won\xe2\x80\x99t hurt this much.'
b'I remember when I thought forever meant forever.'
b'I love you more than I love myself.'
b'The world is a beautiful place and I am no longer afraid to die.'
b'If it is killing you, you are still alive.'
b'Gave her my heart but she wanted my soul.'
b'You broke my heart...\nbut I still love you with all the pieces.'
b'These wounds you have created will never heal.'
b'I lost myself in you.'
b'Waiting for the courage to end it all.'
b'Real love never dies.'
b'I miss the sound of your voice.'
b'Save me from myself.'
b'Feeling hopeless but part of me is still hoping.'
b"I'm sorry for your pain, but nothing beautiful grows without breaking first."
b'Tired of shit not killing me and only making me stronger.'
b'I\xe2\x80\x99ll let you destroy me before I give up.'
b"Every day I've fought to get through without you is a victory I never wanted to win."
b'I love you but you make me so sad.'
b"Please don't let me go."
b'Tired but still trying.'
b'Maybe you\xe2\x80\x99re too good for me.'
b'I hope you\xe2\x80\x99re thinking of me too.'
b'How many times can I fall in love with the same person?'
b'Can I love you until I die?'
b'Save me from this feeling of missing you.'
b"I don't hide anything from you, but when you make me sad, I don't tell you."
b'I could never love like this again.'
b'I don\xe2\x80\x99t care if it\xe2\x80\x99s a lie, just tell me you miss me.'
b'Maybe we all want someone that makes us realize we are worth fighting for.'
b'She used to make me happy with her words.'
b'Honest feelings and bad timing make the most painful combination.'
b'The demons inside me tell me bad things.'
b'Fake happiness is the worst sadness.'
b'Real love is never a waste of time.'
b'I don\xe2\x80\x99t want her to see the sadness in my eyes.'
b'Real depression is when you stop loving the things you love.'
b'It\xe2\x80\x99s so attractive when someone is all about you and isn\xe2\x80\x99t afraid to show it.'
b'I knew I loved you when I started making excuses for the ways you hurt me.'
b'I lost my mind waiting for you to make up yours.'
b'Isolation is so comfortable yet so damaging.'
b'I work so hard for you to remember me that I\xe2\x80\x99m forgetting myself.'
b'Lost in my mind but I look like I\xe2\x80\x99m fine.'
b"Though I'm always sad and lonely, I could never tell you that I'm breaking slowly."
b'Sorry to those I hurt while I was hurting.'
b'I hurt myself today, to see if I still feel.'
b'I wish time had better timing for you and me.'
b'Go ahead and watch my heart burn.'
b'In this life I have loved and been loved in such a way that death has lost all its power.'
b"I feel most alone when I'm thinking of you."
b'Cross my heart and hope to die.'
b'After losing all I\xe2\x80\x99ve lost, the best part is you\xe2\x80\x99re still here...'
b'I\xe2\x80\x99m in so much pain.'
b'When I feel your love it reminds me that all this pain and suffering is worth it...'
b'Too weird to live, too rare to die.'
b'Please stay.'
b'Gave her my heart but she wanted my soul.'
b'Are you insane like me?\nBeen through pain like me?'
b'When love becomes everything, life becomes nothing.'
b'Though it hurts like hell, I cannot get enough. So please, haunt me until the day I die.'
b'We\xe2\x80\x99re all a little dead inside.'
b'Chronically depressed and you\xe2\x80\x99re the only antidote.'
b'I love you, but I hate myself.'
b'There\xe2\x80\x99s more to life than love, but I don\xe2\x80\x99t care much for that stuff.'
b'I wish I was kissing you instead of missing you.'
b'I\xe2\x80\x99m so in love it hurts.'
b'The more you love them the more they can hurt you.'
b'Hidden heartbreak.'
b'My heart hurts.'
b'First it hurts, then it changes you.'
b'The truth may hurt for a little while but a lie hurts forever.'
b'Salt my wound because I can\xe2\x80\x99t heal the way I feel about you.'
b'She loves me, she loves me not.'
b'I survive every day by thinking of you, and then I die doing just the same.'
b'It is perhaps the rarest thing in the world to love and be loved in equal measure.'
b'I still somehow hold so much love for you in this broken heart of mine.'
b'I want to be happy but something inside me screams that I do not deserve it.'
b'I just want to feel for once that I belong.'
b'Maybe if my heart stops beating it won\xe2\x80\x99t hurt this much.'
b'I miss you.'
b'I don\xe2\x80\x99t even know myself at all, I thought I would be happy by now.'
b'In the middle of a war between my heart and my mind.'
